Class MetamapTokenization

    MetaMap tokenization routines.

    A re-implementation of Alan Aronson's Metamap Tokenization in Java. (orignal prolog source: metamap_tokenization.pl)

    Created: Mon Oct 22 16:50:58 2001
    Version:
